	exit
	--------------Plan/Look/Move View Frame------------
	frame .planViewFrame at x 0 ymax.centerButton - 0.1 width 44
		rToggle .planTog |Plan| tagwid 3 at xmin ymin call |!this.inactiveButtonView(1)|
		rToggle .lookTog |Look| tagwid 4 at xmax ymin call |!this.inactiveButtonView(2)|
		rToggle .moveTog |Move| tagwid 4 at xmax ymin call |!this.inactiveButtonView(2)|
