		button .viewU |U| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg LightGold tooltip 'Up' call '!this.planViewMethod(|U|)'
		button .viewD |D| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin tooltip 'Down' call '!this.planViewMethod(|D|)'
	exit

---------------------Piping Tools----------------------
	frame .pipingFoldup foldup 'PIPING TOOLS' at x 0 ymax + 0.1 width.forwBackwFrame
