				button .dirN |N| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg 88 tooltip 'Direction toward North' call |DIR N|
				button .dirS |S| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg ivory tooltip 'Direction toward South' call |DIR S|
				button .dirE |E| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg 28 tooltip 'Direction toward East' call |DIR E|
				button .dirW |W| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg lightblue tooltip 'Direction toward West' call |DIR W|
				button .dirU |U| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin backg LightGold tooltip 'Direction toward Up' call |DIR U|
				button .dirD |D| width 2 hei 1 at xmax ymin tooltip 'Direction toward Down' call |DIR D|
				
