					button .spool150 |150| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |!this.spoolMethod(150)|
					button .spool200 |200| width 3 at x 0 ymax hei 1 call |!this.spoolMethod(200)|
					button .spool300 |300| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |!this.spoolMethod(300)|
					button .spool500 |500| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |!this.spoolMethod(500)|
					
					text .spoolCust1 at xmax.spool150 + 0.5 ymin.spool150 + 0.1 width 5 is REAL
