					button .spoolCust4butt || width 1.2 at xmax ymin.spoolCust4 call |!this.spoolMethod(!this.spoolCust4.val)|
					--- Nice Butt...on!
					rToggle .spoolSelector |SPOOL| tagwid 5 at xmax.spoolCust3butt + 1 ymin.spoolCust3butt
					rToggle .distSelector |DIST| tagwid 4 at xmax + 0.5 ymin
