					button .rotate60 |60°| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |CALLP MROTATE 60|
					button .rotate90 |90°| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |CALLP MROTATE 90|
					button .rotate180 |180°| width 3 at xmax ymin hei 1 call |CALLP MROTATE 180|
